    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant signs of age and neglect, including widespread rust, several large dents, and heavily faded paint. Inside, the cabin has seen better days, with noticeable tears in the seating and non-functional electronics. Most importantly, the car requires major mechanical attention and is not currently roadworthy, making it best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a project or for use as a parts donor.",
